        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>參照了<a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/basic-syntax/">這個網站</a>來測試Markdown的展示效果。</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="標題"><a href="#標題" class="headerlink" title="標題"></a>標題</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Heading level 1</span><br><span class="line">## Heading level 2</span><br><span class="line">### Heading level 3</span><br><span class="line">#### Heading level 4</span><br><span class="line">##### Heading level 5</span><br><span class="line">// #後要空格、標題後要換行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Heading-level-1"><a href="#Heading-level-1" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 1"></a>Heading level 1</h1><h2 id="Heading-level-2"><a href="#Heading-level-2" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 2"></a>Heading level 2</h2><h3 id="Heading-level-3"><a href="#Heading-level-3" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 3"></a>Heading level 3</h3><h4 id="Heading-level-4"><a href="#Heading-level-4" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 4"></a>Heading level 4</h4><h5 id="Heading-level-5"><a href="#Heading-level-5" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 5"></a>Heading level 5</h5><h1 id="粗體"><a href="#粗體" class="headerlink" title="粗體"></a>粗體</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**Bold text**</span><br><span class="line">__Bold text__</span><br><span class="line">// 可以併用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Bold text</strong><br><strong>Bold text</strong></p><h1 id="斜體"><a href="#斜體" class="headerlink" title="斜體"></a>斜體</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*Italic text*</span><br><span class="line">_Italic text_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>Italic text</em><br><em>Italic text</em></p><h1 id="刪除線"><a href="#刪除線" class="headerlink" title="刪除線"></a>刪除線</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~刪除~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><del>刪除</del></p><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; 你好，再見</span><br><span class="line">// 可以引用再引用</span><br><span class="line">// 引用的內文也可以套用其他語法</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>你好，再見</p></blockquote><h1 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. First item</span><br><span class="line">2. Second item</span><br><span class="line">3. Third item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>First item</li><li>Second item</li><li>Third item</li></ol><h1 id="無序列表"><a href="#無序列表" class="headerlink" title="無序列表"></a>無序列表</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- First item</span><br><span class="line">- Second item</span><br><span class="line">- Third item</span><br><span class="line">    - Indented item</span><br><span class="line">    - Indented item</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* First item</span><br><span class="line">* Second item</span><br><span class="line">* Third item</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ First item</span><br><span class="line">+ Second item</span><br><span class="line">+ Third item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>First item</li><li>Second item</li><li>Third item<ul><li>Indented item</li><li>Indented item</li></ul></li></ul><ul><li>First item</li><li>Second item</li><li>Third item</li></ul><ul><li>First item</li><li>Second item</li><li>Third item</li></ul><h1 id="連結"><a href="#連結" class="headerlink" title="連結"></a>連結</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Markdown的參考網站是[這個](&lt;https://www.markdownguide.org&gt;)。</span><br><span class="line">&lt;https://www.markdownguide.org&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Markdown的參考網站是<a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/">這個</a>。<br><a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/">https://www.markdownguide.org</a></p><h1 id="圖片"><a href="#圖片" class="headerlink" title="圖片"></a>圖片</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 使用Local Files新增圖片</span><br><span class="line">![acnhss](source/images/acnh001.jpeg)</span><br><span class="line">- 使用URL新增圖片</span><br><span class="line">![acnhss](https://images.plurk.com/R5Kxh0rvyKOAQHzuK3LHA.jpg &quot;動森截圖&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">- 在圖片上增加連結</span><br><span class="line">[![acnhss](https://images.plurk.com/R5Kxh0rvyKOAQHzuK3LHA.jpg &quot;動森截圖&quot;)](https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/acbaa/index.html)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>使用Local Files新增圖片<br><img src="/source/images/acnh001.jpeg" alt="acnhss"></li><li>使用URL新增圖片<br><img src="https://images.plurk.com/R5Kxh0rvyKOAQHzuK3LHA.jpg" alt="acnhss" title="動森截圖"></li><li>在圖片上增加連結<br><a href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/acbaa/index.html"><img src="https://images.plurk.com/R5Kxh0rvyKOAQHzuK3LHA.jpg" alt="acnhss" title="動森截圖"></a></li></ul><h1 id="程式碼"><a href="#程式碼" class="headerlink" title="程式碼"></a>程式碼</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`Code`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="參考文獻"><a href="#參考文獻" class="headerlink" title="參考文獻"></a>參考文獻</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">In a hole in the ground there lived a hobbit. Not a nasty, dirty, wet hole, filled with the ends</span><br><span class="line">of worms and an oozy smell, nor yet a dry, bare, sandy hole with nothing in it to sit down on or to</span><br><span class="line">eat: it was a [hobbit-hole][1], and that means comfort.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[1]: &lt;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hobbit#Lifestyle&gt; &quot;Hobbit lifestyles&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>In a hole in the ground there lived a hobbit. Not a nasty, dirty, wet hole, filled with the ends<br>of worms and an oozy smell, nor yet a dry, bare, sandy hole with nothing in it to sit down on or to<br>eat: it was a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hobbit#Lifestyle" title="Hobbit lifestyles">hobbit-hole</a>, and that means comfort.</p><h1 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 標題1 | 標題2 | 標題3 |</span><br><span class="line">| :------ | :------: | ------: |</span><br><span class="line">| 置左 | 置中 | 置右 |</span><br><span class="line">| 這是測試文字 |  這是測試文字 | 這是測試文字 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">標題1</th><th align="center">標題2</th><th align="right">標題3</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">置左</td><td align="center">置中</td><td align="right">置右</td></tr><tr><td align="left">這是測試文字</td><td align="center">這是測試文字</td><td align="right">這是測試文字</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
